{"thig2.10:0.1":"Therigatha 2.10 ","thig2.10:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thig2.10:0.3":"Samatherigatha ","thig2.10:1.1":"“Catukkhattum pancakkhattum, ","thig2.10:1.2":"vihara upanikkhamim; ","thig2.10:1.3":"Aladdha cetaso santim, ","thig2.10:1.4":"citte avasavattini; ","thig2.10:1.5":"Tassa me atthami ratti, ","thig2.10:1.6":"yato tanha samuhata. ","thig2.10:2.1":"Bahuhi dukkhadhammehi, ","thig2.10:2.2":"appamadarataya me; ","thig2.10:2.3":"Tanhakkhayo anuppatto, ","thig2.10:2.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thig2.10:3.1":"… Sama theri …. ","thig2.10:4.1":"Dukanipato nitthito. "}